  |     Summary                                                             |
  |   -------------------------------------------------------------------   |
  |                                                                         |
  |   Wreckin' Ball Adventure is a 2.5D platformer with physics-based       |
  |   puzzles cleverly incorporated in 60 levels. Beat story mode solo or   |
  |   bring up to 3 friends! You can roll, jump or swing using your         |
  |   trusty grappling hook. Plan your way - wreck through walls, avoid     |
  |   threats and escape. Gather orbs and collect stars to unlock stages.   |
  |   Discover the dark secret of evil SuperCom and roll your way out of    |
  |   jail!                                                                 |
  |                                                                         |
  |   * 60 levels in story mode;                                            |
  |                                                                         |
  |   * Playground mode where you can practice your skills;                 |
  |                                                                         |
  |   * Endless mode where you have only one task - to survive as long as   |
  |     you can. Preferably longer than your friends;                       |
  |                                                                         |
  |   * All modes are available in solo or local co-op for up to 4          |
  |     players                                                             |
  |                                                                         |
  |   Languages: English.                                                   |
